CustomField.description: Please fill in the form any contracts, MSAs, countersigned anything that you can think of that have the following qualities * A significant departure from our standard paper (e.g. Their paper, lots and lots of redlines, lots of addendums) * Increases/Uncapped liability * Increase in SLA * Changes/Clarifications to contract exit criterion (e.g. arbitrary contract terminations, release from the contract without cause).
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Notes regarding the nature of the changes/redlines/etc.
CustomField.label: Contract notes
